/**
 * A class for holding a set of functions to add/update content
 * for all modules
 *
 * @category Main
 * @package  Loris
 * @author   Rathi Sekaran <sekaranrathi@gmail.com>
 * @license  Loris license
 * @link     https://www.github.com/aces/Loris-Trunk/
